<P>
   MEXICO-WHALES-$ADV26 _ TIJUANA, Mexico _ To some, protecting the
gray whales that mate and give birth warm-water lagoon near here is
like a religion. It may sound a little wacky, but their passion was
enough to cause the Mexican government and Japan's Mitsubishi Corp.
to suddenly scrap plans to build a new salt mining factory on the
lagoon _ despite the fact that an environmental study showed that
it would not harm the whales. (Ferriss).
</P>
