<P>
   RUSSIA-SECURITY-$ADV26 _ MOSCOW _ Russians go to the polls today
for only the second time in their history to elect a president. It
will be anti-climactic because acting President Vladimir Putin is
the runaway victor. We take a good look at what the United States
and the West may expect from the new guy with access to the launch
codes for the world's second largest nuclear arsenal. (Coker).
</P>
<P>
   With RUSSIA-AID-$ADV26 _ WASHINGTON _ Vladimir Putin has got the
