<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-19 17:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1673 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-TV-NOTEBOOK-2TAKES-NY     03-19 0983
