<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-19 18:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1699 &Cx1f; tab-z
u l BC-CNS-SEX-CRIMES &LR;      03-19 1079
