<P>
   A report in the Campaign Briefing column sent on Thursday, March
16 about an election challenge to Senator Edward M. Kennedy of
Massachusetts by Jack E. Robinson III referred incorrectly in some
copies to the number of years Mr. Kennedy has served. It is 38, not
36.
