   BC-CIR-GEEK-NOTES-NYT (moved Wednesday, March 15)
</P>
<P>
   A Circuits column sent on Wednesday, March 15 about the online
version of the Oxford English Dictionary misstated the price of
institutional subscriptions. They start at $795 and depend on the
customer's size, the number of users and other factors; there is no
universal price.
